        {
            "id": "https://vervallsweg.github.io/cast-web/Help.html",
            "url": "https://vervallsweg.github.io/cast-web/Help.html",
            "title": "Help",
            "content_html": "<p>So, you have a problem with cast-web? Don't worry!</p>\n<p>First check the <a href=\"#INTERNAL_LINK#/post/11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">FAQ</a>.</p>\n<p>Then have a quick look at the <a href=\"https://community.smartthings.com/t/release-cast-web-0-2-chromecast-device-handler-smartapps/88038\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SmartThings community forum thread</a>.</p>\n<p>If you cannot find the answer there, just signup and ask your question on <a href=\"https://community.smartthings.com/t/release-cast-web-0-2-chromecast-device-handler-smartapps/88038\">the forum</a>.</p>\n<h2>Found a bug?</h2>\n<p>Just open an issue on the GitHub repo. Make sure that it's the right one. For the api go to cast-web-api for the DTH and Smartapp it's smartthings.</p>",
            "image": "https://vervallsweg.github.io/cast-web/media/posts/4/",
            "author": {
                "name": "vervallsweg"
